videos.headline: Jarrett Stidham: 'We're fighting for one another'
videos.description: Baylor QB Jarrett Stidham breaks down his performance in the Bears' 31-24 win over Kansas State and why his team can face the challenge of their remaining Big 12 schedule.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Jarett Stidham on win over Kansas State) 2015/11/05 SC

videos.headline: INT secures Baylor's win over Kansas State
videos.description: Baylor's interception of Kansas State QB Kody Cook on the final drive and QB Jarrett Stidham's 419 passing yards and three touchdowns lead the No. 6 Bears to a 31-24 win over the Wildcats. Baylor improves to 8-0 on the season.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (SC Baylor-Kansas State) 2015/11/05 ESHEET SportsCenter
